Package org.sd.fsm

Interface Summary
FSM Finite state machine
Generator An fsm generator based on example sequences.
Grammar Definition of valid states and transitions.
Rule Marker interface for a rule that defines states.
State
StateDecoder Decode a state by dumping its tokens into a tree.
Token Wrapper around and marker interface for a token of input to an FSM.
 

Class Summary
Validator A validator using an fsm for token sequences.
